Entry-Name: .description

This test aims to check the reference widget.

The test :
* loads the tests projects released with the Sirius test product,
* opens the test diagram,
* selects the reference viewpoint,
* selects an element in the diagram,
* checks the properties view  of a reference widget :
 - checks the label,
 - checks the value.
